song.title: Finding Myself (Demo Edit)
song.info:
My first song for Nerve. I just joined Nerve artgroup. Also the second song on my new album "Broken." "Saturation (Part I)" was the first song on the album.
This song is a shortened version of my upcoming song, Finding Myself. Look out for it, but I may never release a new version of this song. Hope you like this one!
